Package org.tensorics.core.tensorbacked

Class AbstractTensorbacked<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorics.core.tensorbacked.AbstractTensorbacked<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the elements of the tensor, which backs this class
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Tensorbacked<E>
    public abstract class AbstractTensorbacked<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tensorbacked<E>, java.io.Serializable
    An abstract class for classes that are backed by a tensor. The purpose of such classes is that they can be used for calculations just in the same way (or at least in a similar way) as tensors themselves.
    See Also:
